When to use await ---> When We do Back ground actives or  we want thing or if there any statement retun the promise we have to use awaite

“async makes a function return a Promise, and await pauses execution until the Promise resolves
📦 Promise → Box with future value

🎟 async → Permission to use await

⏳ await → Wait until value comes

PlayWright Run:-
1. npx playwright test
2. npx playwright show-report
3. npx playwright --headed
4. npx playwright test MyTest1.spec.ts --project=chromium
5. npx playwright test MyTest1.spec.ts
6. npx playwright test MyTest1.spec.ts MyTest.spec.ts
7. npx playwright test -g "verify" (matching Of title like wherever verify is that test case will excute)
8. npx playwright test --ui